    @template    block_feedback_tracker/manage

    Tools landing page — capability-gated link list.

    Context variables required:
    * heading   Page heading
    * links     Array of {url, label}

    Example context (json):
    {
        "heading": "Feedback Flow — tools",
        "links": [
            {"url": "/blocks/feedback_tracker/pages/calendar_editor.php", "label": "Calendar editor"},
            {"url": "/blocks/feedback_tracker/pages/audit_log.php",      "label": "Audit log"}
        ]
    }
}}
<h2>{{heading}}</h2>
<ul class="bft-tools-list">
    {{#links}}
        <li><a href="{{url}}">{{label}}</a></li>
    {{/links}}
</ul>
